3ï¸âƒ£ Loop Trick

Old JS problem:

for (var i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  setTimeout(() => console.log(i), 1000);
}


Output:

3
3
3


Because var shares the same variable.

Correct version:

for (let i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
  setTimeout(() => console.log(i), 1000);
}


Output:

0
1
2


