ğŸ§ª Short Interview Answers

Q: Difference between var, let, and const?

var â†’ function scoped, hoisted, redeclarable

let â†’ block scoped, no redeclaration, TDZ

const â†’ block scoped, no reassignment, TDZ

ğŸ¯ Golden Rule (Real Developer Rule)
// 80% of the time
